e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞飯先係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太多鋪用冰鮮雞，用都唔緊要仲要未完全解晒凍就用，搞到好難食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4822f7f9869f36075609bc4c472b1b4d68d4b5c","tid":62642,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"有無巴打鍾意鹹蛋/鹹魚肉餅飯？<br />\n我個個禮拜都會最少食一次。"},{"pid":"7fb5593f51bc768f98b75c8bb80cae22194a174f","tid":62642,"uid":4150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/01/135925_5674910437db00dfd51e716a229b0678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F01%2F135925_5674910437db00dfd51e716a229b0678.jpg&h=d59777eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本帥認同</blockquote><br />\n二哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都同意鳳爪排骨飯最好食，不過冇豉油就不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重點唔係個豉油，係排骨同鳳爪嘅肉汁出嚟入左啲飯度，嗰個味道先係最好食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多"},{"pid":"9c85e6a34585bb8faab78dba0c84cd0d4a9beeee","tid":62642,"uid":5555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔食鳳爪嘅我都好鐘意呢個飯"},{"pid":"ef75e73dda3079ffd1781cfb196a2c1b581e70b1","tid":62642,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/01/135925_5674910437db00dfd51e716a229b0678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F01%2F135925_5674910437db00dfd51e716a229b0678.jpg&h=d59777eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n